<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-21-0351 </DOCNO><TEXT>This volume aims to provide up-to-date information on recent researchand development in computer science and technology in Japan. In viewof the rapid developments in these fields and the urgent demand for moredetailed information about Japanese activities and achievements, it hasbeen decided to concentrate on only a few selected topics in each volume.The topics covered will change each year so as to obtain adequate coverageof a broad range of activities over a period of a few years. This editionshould not only contribute to the international understanding of technicaldevelopments in Japan, but also shed light on the cultural backgroundto these theoretical and practical developments.</TEXT></DOC>